  "title": "Senior Software Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our Client:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>AWS, VB</strong></li><li><strong>Monday- Friday: 9am - 6pm</strong></li><li><strong>1 day WFH</strong></li><li><strong>Supply Chain Technology</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop modular, production-ready code deployable on cloud platforms (AWS, GCP, Azure) or on-premise.</li><li>Redesign and improve existing systems to turn complex business requirements into scalable software components.</li><li>Build  system components that integrate research models into reliable, scalable business solutions.</li><li>Apply and improve best practices in software architecture, development workflows, coding standards, and DevOps/MLOps.</li><li>Review code and ensure all deliverables meet performance, security, and maintainability standards.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Operations Research.</li><li>Strong Python skills and familiarity with SQL/NoSQL databases (MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB).</li><li>Experience with unit/integration testing.</li><li>Skilled in microservices, API design, and system architecture.</li><li>4+ years in software engineering with experience deploying production systems.</li><li>Hands-on experience deploying infrastructure as code on at least one major cloud platform.</li><li>Experience deploying applications using Docker, Kubernetes, and CI/CD pipelines.</li><li><strong>Experience deploying AI models</strong> with orchestration tools (Airflow, Prefect, Ray) and reporting tools (Tableau, Holistics) is a plus.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>For interested applicants, please click \"APPLY NOW\"</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented to us collecting, using, retaining, and disclosing your personal information to prospective employers for their consideration.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>EA Personnel Name: Elsa Adam | EA Reg No: R22109576</strong><br /><strong>JTE Recruit Pte Ltd | EA License No: 14C7215</strong></p>",
